{
  "stem": "22979.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I had to mention them because I remember that one of my girlfriends worked also-- close to Auschwitz, there was a-- a little village, and they had to tore down the houses because they-- I don't know if they built something else or not.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she told me that these Ukrainian women-- and they were about, she said, 10 in this kommando-- they were worse than the German kapos there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she suffered this time physically very much from them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's only-- the one time what I heard about this-- what I saw after zahlappell when-- that-- [? they ?] [? were-- ?] because they were dressed even different.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had the striped uniforms, and we and the people who came already-- like I said, the Hungarian to camp-- they had civilian clothing with the cross-- a red, you know, cross in the back so you could recognize them even, you know, they were Caucasian, white like the rest.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not like here-- the races in color.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So just that, what I want to say about the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Although, you know, how-- how very sorry we were toward those poor Russian POWs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were mixed-- Ukraine, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Belarus, ?] Latvians, in one together who were killed, you know, by the thousands before we came.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you're saying the some of the Ukrainian women had the worst jobs--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But other Ukrainian women were in the status of, like, a kapo, also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not kapo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were foremens, but not kapos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kapo-- a kapo was a head of the foremen, and we were, you know, the workers, the slave workers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they worked too-- no compare.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they suffered the same, you know, destiny like we do it-- we did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they did not gas the Aryans.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
